To make all mass point cards for exo_WG, simply type make.

To make all mass point cards for only the leptonic final state type make wgtolnu
To make all mass point cards for only the hadronic final state type make wgtojj

The masses and widths that are considered can be modified by editing the 
'MASS_POINTS' and 'WIDTHS' lists at the top of the make_all_cards.py script

The commands in the Makefile can be used as templates for other use cases
